videos.description: Malik Dunbar drives the lane, gathers and puts up a tough shot for an and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Auburn's Dunbar banks in basket through contact

videos.description: Bryce Brown knocks down a corner 3-pointer to put Auburn up 36-16 on Washington.
videos.headline: Brown 3-pointer puts Auburn up 20 on Washington

videos.description: Matisse Thybulle drives the lane and rises up for a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Thybulle throws down on Auburn defender

videos.description: Jared Harper drives the lane and tosses a lob to Malik Dunbar who finishes with a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Dunbar throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Nahziah Carter comes up with a steal and finishes at the other end with a windmill slam.
videos.headline: Washington's Carter throws down windmill dunk
